  "circuit": {
    "description": "RelayDT energised regime: vSrc=10V across coil drives I_coil=0.1A > pullInI=0.05A, contact NO closes (A1<->B1) and NC opens (A1<->C1). vTest=1V probes the contact loop through rLoadB (on B1) and rLoadC (on C1) so the nets are not floating.",
